gomodel:SYNGO_2648  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: LTP induction was enhanced in PTPRD KO mice.. Experimental description: Materials and methods\nGeneration of Ptprd-/- mice\nChimeric mice were generated using the targeted ES clones by the aggregation method. Male chimeras were mated with C57BL/6J females, and homozygous mutant mice were obtained by intercrossing the heterozygous." ;
